#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.dolphin-plugins.metainfo.xml:10
msgid ""
"These plugins integrate Dolphin with the revision control systems Bazaar, "
"Mercurial and Git. A Dropbox plugin gives action items to keep your files "
"synced to the Dropbox service. A disk image integration plugin adds a mount "
"or unmount action."
msgstr ""
"Plugin-plugin tersebut mengintegrasikan Dolphin dengan sistem kendali revisi "
"Bazaar, Mercurial dan Git. Sebuah plugin Dropbox memberikan item aksi untuk "
"tetap menjaga file-filemu tersinkron ke layanan Dropbox. Sebuah plugin "
"integrasi citra disk menambahkan aksi kait (mount) dan lepaskan kaitan "
"(unmount)."
